metadata.name: HATCHING CROCODOOD
metadata.description:
Hey Doods, welcome to the Den.  
  
We’re Crocoods, a collection of 6,000 unique NFTs existing deep underground within the swampy depths of the Metaverse. Our digital art is revealing on April 24th, 2022 and will be owned by only the coolest and finest of doods.  
  
As always, don’t forget to be nice. be kind. be dood.
